data.description: Your new home awaits in Tre Vicino. This fantastic gated community is perfectly located in the heart of Chandler with 2 separate pool areas for yourself and guests. Built in 2020, this property features 4 generously sized bedrooms, 3.5 baths and almost 2200 sqft. First floor has its own guest suite with full bath and closet. 2nd floor has an open concept kitchen with granite counters, large island, and walk in pantry. It opens to the spacious living area great for entertaining. You even have your own private balcony to relax on. 3rd floor features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths including the master suite with walk in closet, dual sinks and walk-in shower. Upgraded stair railing, smart home features, 2 car garage and front courtyard artificial turf are just a few great additions to this home. Situated on a premium lot and located within steps from the green belt common area within the community. Close to shopping, downtown Chandler entertainment and the 202 freeway.
